trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting a file name.
trans-unit.target: Gir et brukergrensesnitt for å velge et filnavn.

trans-unit.source: FileNameEditor provides a file selection dialog box for file name selection and editing.
trans-unit.target: FileNameEditor inneholder en dialogboks for valg for valg av fil og redigere.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Edits the specified object using the editor style provided by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*> method.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer det angitte objektet ved hjelp av redigeringsprogrammet-stil fra den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: A service provider is provided so that any required editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: En leverandør er angitt slik at alle nødvendige redigering tjenester kan hentes.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A service provider object through which editing services may be obtained.
trans-unit.target: En leverandør Webtjenesteobjektet som redigering services kan hentes.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the value being edited.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av verdien som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The new value of the object.
If the value of the object hasn't changed, this should return the same object it was passed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, kan dette vil returnere det samme objektet det ble sendt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue*> method.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering som brukes av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue*>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A> method is not supported, this method will return <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A>metoden støttes ikke, denne metoden tilbakestiller <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> values indicating the provided editing style.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref> verdier som angir det angitte redigering stil.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the open file dialog when it is created.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer dialogboksen Åpne Da den ble opprettet.

trans-unit.source: This method configures the dialog box with a generic file filter and title.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden konfigurerer dialogboksen med en generell filfilter og tittel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.OpenFileDialog"></xref> to use to select a file name.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> bruke til å velge et filnavn.
